Name: Contrasted
About the game: Contrasted is a Single player co-op platformer with non-stop action. Use one hand to control each character, moving them around the levels while avoiding obstacles and solving puzzles to find your way out. Inspired by games like Super meatboy and N++, Contrasted is guaranteed to bring you hours of exciting challenging frustrating gaming like never before.
